      <title>Beach Point 的 Bowron 和 Apollo 的 Grewal 谈论困境投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/sinjin-bowron-akila-grewal-on-distressed-investing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Beach Point Capital Management 投资组合经理 Sinjin Bowron 表示，现在的投资是安全资产和压力资产的混合，而 Apollo Global Management 合伙人兼全球信贷产品主管 Akila Grewal 预计 2025 年的压力会更大。他们与 Sonali Basak 就“实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/sinjin-bowron-akila-grewal-on-distressed-investing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 20:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
