      <title>加拿大企业受益于美国股市上涨，ETF 规模去年飙升逾 5,000 亿加元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/etfs-surge-past-c-500-billion-in-canada-as-buyers-ride-us-equity-rally</link>
