      <title>零日期权在标普 500 指数中占据主导地位，成为最受欢迎的期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/zero-day-options-are-most-popular-on-s-p-500-as-dominance-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔 500 指数的零日期权在第四季度首次超过其他所有到期期权的总和，这是标志着短期合约主导地位日益增强的最新里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/zero-day-options-are-most-popular-on-s-p-500-as-dominance-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 20:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
